creator: PhonixDev
descriptionHtml:
Maha360 app is the project of Phonix Dev Pvt ltd. This is mainly made to help of MSBTE diploma, D pharma, and SPPU engineering, MBA students for scoring good marks in the exam.

Features and content in-app are as follow:

Features for MSBTE Diploma and D pharma Students
You can able to Download and read study material are as follow :

Solved Manuals
Notes made by Maha360 App teachers and Experts
MCQ of Online subjects
IMP questions for Oral, Practical and Exam [ Included In notes ]
Syllabus of all subjects
Model answer paper
Question paper
Separate space for MSBTE diploma 1st-year students and common subjects
D pharma 1st & 2nd-year Question paper, Model answer, and syllabus


Features for SPPU Engineering and MBA Students:
You can able to Download and read study material are as follow :

Question paper of all subjects with pattern 2012,2013,2015,2019
Important notes for engineering students
Question paper of all elective subjects
MBA 1st,2nd,3rd, and 4th semester question paper and notes

Maha360 app - Study forever
Keep learning! Keep growing!

Disclaimer -
This is not an official app of MSBTE and SPPU. This App is only made for educational purpose and help students to the practice for exams related Computer. We are not affiliated with MSBTE and entity, services, or person.

Any kind of query, please contact us.
Email - phonixdev007@gmail.com
